item.description:
Hi Westport Boston Terrier Meetup Members
We are going to meetup at the Westport Town Beach! If the weather is too cold we will meet at Dighton Rock State Park! I will be emailing you just before the event.
The 6th of Noverber is on a SATURDAY!
DIRECTIONS TO THE WESTPORT TOWN BEACH:
Rte88 toward Horsneck Beach
Take a right just past the bridge-this will lead you onto Cherry and Webb Lane
Follow Cherry and Webb Lane to the end.Parking for the beach is on your left!
Linda and Bob
